des: say 'find tutor' after the prompt you can say 'find a tutor for {classAbbreviation} num {classNumber} ' replacing the words inside the brackets with your own. You will then be prompted as to whether or not you would like to get the tutors email, say 'request email' and alexa will tell you the tutors email.
